00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:48.980
Yanımda ol!  

00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:52.150
Anne!  

00:16:52.150 --> 00:16:53.400
Hanımefendi.  

00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:54.860
Anne!  

